These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, indie, house
1. the fan of house is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | indie | house |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
3 different pets are kept: turtle, cat, dog
1. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the dog is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Pet   | turtle | dog | cat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, quad-bike, subway
1. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | ship | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, drawing, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | card-games | drawing | magic-tricks |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, country, dubstep
1. the fan of dubstep is on the far right##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | country | dubstep |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, drama, comedy
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | drama | comedy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite, iced-tea
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |       2       |  3  |
| Beverage   | mirinda | sprite | iced-tea |

 #################################

 
