.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, camping
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
2. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | card-games | camping | board-games |

